9. 可以直接丟給 Codex 的完整 prompt

你可以複製這段：

I want to build a completely free personal academic portfolio website.

Please create a Next.js project using TypeScript and Tailwind CSS.

Deployment target:
- Vercel free Hobby plan
- No paid services
- No backend or database
- No paid APIs

Website structure:
1. Hero section
   - Name: Cheng-Hsuan Chien
   - Subtitle: Master's student in Communication Engineering and Signal Processing
   - Buttons: Email, GitHub, CV

2. About section
   - Use placeholder text for now

3. Research section
   - Topics:
     - Sparse array design
     - Signal processing
     - Array optimization
     - Wireless communications

4. Projects section
   - Use reusable project cards
   - Put project data in a separate TypeScript array

5. Publications section
   - Use reusable publication cards
   - Put publication data in a separate TypeScript array

6. Contact section
   - Use mailto link only
   - Do not implement a backend contact form

Design:
- Clean, minimal, academic, modern
- Responsive for mobile and desktop
- Good spacing and typography
- Avoid heavy animations

Implementation requirements:
- Use reusable components
- Keep the code easy to edit
- Add README.md with:
  - how to run locally
  - how to build
  - how to deploy to Vercel
- Make sure npm run build passes

我的建議是你先不要買網域，先用免費的 vercel.app 或 github.io 網址把網站做起來。等你真的要放在 CV、論文頁、求職履歷上，再考慮花一年幾百塊台幣買自己的 domain。
